{"_id":"ucsr4x30zje","name":"Limited Degree","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>Your Affliction is limited to no more than two degrees of effect. With two applications of this modifier, it is limited to no more than one degree of effect.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"3yymn5l2iah","name":"Activation","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> FLAT (Fixed)<br/><hr/><p>A power with this flaw requires an action to prepare or activate before any of its effects are usable. Move action is –1 point, standard action is –2 points.</p><p>Flat -1 or -2 points.</p>","cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":false,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"0a8lbnrfswom","name":"Instant Recovery","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>The target of an Affliction effect with this modifier recovers automatically, no check required, at the end of the round in which the duration ends.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"izbwrhek83m","name":"Check Required","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>An effect with this flaw requires a check of some sort—usually a skill check—with a base difficulty of 10, +1 for each additional rank in Check Required.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"w0q594g8rbh","name":"Concentration","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>Using a Concentration effect requires more concentration than normal. If you are unable to maintain your concentration, the effect ends.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"4a36bxeyy7o","name":"Diminished Range","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>Each rank of this flaw reduces the effect’s range increments by one step.</p><p>Flat -1 point per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"u5ro4s9hlq","name":"Distracting","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>Using a Distracting effect requires so much concentration or effort that you are vulnerable until the start of your next turn.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"bb4smxy09jd","name":"Grab-Based","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>An attack with this flaw requires you to successfully grab and hold a target before the effect can be used.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"i461p490rpo","name":"Increased Action","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>Each rank of this flaw increases the action required to use an effect by one step (Free to Move, Move to Standard, etc.).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"vtxs3945vv","name":"Limited","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>An effect with this flaw only works under certain circumstances, or has a significant restriction on its use.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"wt3pk75858k","name":"Noticeable","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> FLAT (Fixed)<br/><hr/><p>A continuous or permanent effect with this flaw is very noticeable (glows, makes a loud noise, etc.).</p><p>Flat -1 point.</p>","cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":false,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"xljbsl4mvie","name":"Quirk","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> FLAT (Fixed)<br/><hr/><p>A Quirk is a minor flaw, often something specific to a character or power, that doesn’t quite rise to the level of a full -1 cost per rank flaw.</p><p>Flat -1 point.</p>","cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":false,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"cfnjtnh6fzq","name":"Reduced Range","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>Each rank of this flaw reduces the range of an effect (Ranged to Close, etc.).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"7391t8fmx9e","name":"Resistible","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>An effect with this flaw allows an additional resistance check, or is resisted by a different defense than usual.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"7yf64upq7i5","name":"Sense-Dependent","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>The target must be able to perceive the effect with a particular sense for it to work.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"jtnlob9q8ss","name":"Side Effect","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>If you fail to use the effect properly, or even if you succeed, you suffer a negative side effect.</p><p>–1 or –2 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"drz1cf6ult","name":"Tiring","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>Using the effect is physically or mentally taxing, causing you to become fatigued.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"rhetor4in1q","name":"Uncontrolled","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>You have no control over when the effect activates or what it does; the GM decides.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"3lfabvgus8w","name":"Unreliable","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>An Unreliable effect only works some of the time (5 uses, or requires a check each time).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"2x9yui2yzd4","name":"Feedback","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>You suffer damage when a manifestation of your effect is damaged.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"gcoy04tu5b","name":"Inaccurate","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>An effect with this flaw is hard to control or wildly inaccurate. Each rank gives you a –2 penalty to attack checks.</p><p>Flat -1 point per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"gfovi9mtn45","name":"Permanent","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> PER RANK<br/><hr/><p>A continuous effect with this flaw becomes permanent in duration. It cannot be turned off and cannot be improved using extra effort.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"rjwr972gbl","name":"Removable","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 1<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> FLAT (Fixed)<br/><hr/><p>Removable applies to the power as a whole. The flaw is worth –1 point per 5 total power points.</p><p>Flat -1 point per 5 points.</p>","cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":false,"value":1,"total":1}}}
{"_id":"bl6ds1r746b","name":"Easily Removable","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<b>[ MODIFIER TYPE: DEFAUT ]</b><br/>&bull; <b>Cost Reduction:</b> 2<br/>&bull; <b>Toggle Type:</b> FLAT (Fixed)<br/><hr/><p>An easily removable power can be taken away with a disarm or grab action. The flaw is worth –2 points per 5 total power points.</p><p>Flat -2 points per 5 points.</p>","cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":false,"value":2,"total":2}}}